Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.98,0:02:03.15,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}蒼い日差し浴びて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.01,0:02:07.51,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}風を切る君に
