Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.22,0:01:53.06,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}涌上心头的 感动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.98,0:02:03.15,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}沐浴着湛蓝的阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.01,0:02:07.51,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}你迎风前行的身姿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.83,0:02:14.19,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}让我陶醉时 目光相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.31,0:02:19.05,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我们齐声欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.90,0:02:26.32,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}就像那 小小漩涡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.19,0:02:33.10,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,1000)\an3}无论何时 都想挥动双手的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.98,0:02:37.39,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}确实是 曾经
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.78,0:02:42.92,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}与你同在的印记
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.67,0:02:47.27,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}永远如 小小漩涡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.68,0:02:57.06,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我们的前方 道路在延伸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.48,0:03:05.79,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}攀上 下一个陡坡后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.58,0:03:10.55,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,1000)}我们再相见吧
